\f0\i [tossing her head]
\f1\i0 . Oh, if it is a wife who has any head for business\'97a wife who has the wit to be a little bit clever\'97\
MRS LINDE.\uc0\u8232 I don\'92t understand it at all, Nora.\
NORA.\uc0\u8232 There is no need you should. I never said I had borrowed the money. I may have got it some other way. 
\f0\i [Lies back on the sofa.]
