NORA.\uc0\u8232 
\f0\i [smiling and humming]
\f1\i0 . That\'92s my affair! 
\f0\i [Walking about the room.]
\f1\i0  It\'92s perfectly glorious to think that we have\'97that Torvald has so much power over so many people. 
