MRS LINDE.\uc0\u8232 Nora, dear\'97!\
RANK.\uc0\u8232 Say it, here he is!\
NORA.\uc0\u8232 
\f0\i [hiding the packet]
\f1\i0 . Hush! Hush! Hush! 
\f0\i [HELMER comes out of his room, with his coat over his arm and his hat in his hand.]
\f1\i0 \
NORA.\uc0\u8232 Well, Torvald dear, have you got rid of him?\
