NORA.\uc0\u8232 
\f0\i [walking up and down the stage]
\f1\i0 . Sometimes one has a tiny little bit of influence, I should hope. Because one is a woman, it does not necessarily follow that\'97. When anyone is in a subordinate position, Mr. Krogstad, they should really be careful to avoid offending anyone who\'97who\'97\
